  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">moderate</span> upgrade for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Starship Defensive Shielding</span>. Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to begin upgrade <VAL_ON>installation process<>.<br><br>The module is flexible, and exact upgrade statistics are <span class=\"name name-special\">unknown</span> until installation is complete.<br><br>Improves <span class=\"name name-stellar\">ship strength</span> for increased combat endurance.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "对<span class=\"name name-technology\">飞船防御护罩</span>的<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">普通</span>提升。使用<VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><>开始<VAL_ON>安装升级<>。<br><br>该模块很灵活，具体升级信息在安装结束前<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">船体强度</span>来提升战斗时的耐久度。",
    "TencentChinese": "对<span class=\"name name-technology\">飞船防御护罩</span>的<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">普通</span>提升。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>开始安装升级。<br><br>提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">船体强度</span>来提升战斗时的耐久度。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">太空船防禦防護罩</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">一般</span>升級。用 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> 開始升級<VAL_ON>安裝程序<>。<br><br>此模組富有彈性，直到安裝完成前，確切的升級數據為<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船強度</span>以便增加戰鬥持久力。"
